176
00:16:23,424 --> 00:16:25,124
愛包ダンスホール
Love-Wrapped Dance Hall

177
00:16:27,424 --> 00:16:29,124
おかわりならもし
If you want a refill

178
00:16:30,424 --> 00:16:32,124
愛包ダンスホール
Love-Wrapped Dance Hall

179
00:16:34,924 --> 00:16:36,024
どうぞ
Here you go

180
